author: strider1919
body: Incredible how $KENDU - a mere meme coin - has continued to sustain its position despite a bear market that is hemorrhaging value (looking at you, ETH).   It’s simple to understand yet difficult to implement: community.  It’s the only thing that can persist in a world of KOLs, cabals, pump & dumps, farming, slow pulls (did I get it all?)…  So glad to be here amongst the conviction and action of our Chads / Chadettes. Our time will come but we’re not concerned with schedules, only impact!

author: KenduGNX
body: I understand where you are coming from but I invite you to take a look at the wider market. This is not a Kendu issue haha.   Also, look at how other communities are dealing with the overall market sentiment and how the Kendu community keeps working and pushing initiatives like the OP.   The Kendu community is continuing to build through the rough conditions and when sentiment turns we will be in prime position to ride the wave to the top. Hope to see you there with us!
